Ndërsa nuk e dimë me siguri nëse ky viru.source_string: While we don't know for sure that this virus will behave the same way as SARS-CoV and MERS-CoV, we can use the information gained from both of these earlier coronaviruses to guide us. In general, because of poor survivability of these coronaviruses on surfaces, there is likely very low risk of spread from products or packaging that are shipped over a period of days or weeks at ambient temperatures. Coronaviruses are generally thought to be spread most often by respiratory droplets. Currently there is no evidence to support transmission of COVID-19 associated with imported goods and there have not been any cases of COVID-19 in the United States associated with imported goods. Information will be provided on the Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) website as it becomes available.

Në Wish, ne jemi të përkushtuar të garan.source_string: At Wish, we are committed to ensuring the safety of our community and addressing any reports we receive regarding inappropriate or unsafe materials or products found listed on our platform.

Në Wish, ne kemi përparësi klientët dhe.source_string:
At Wish, we put customers first and are willing to pay to insure that Wish users receive excellent service. Today, we learned that one of your orders was not prepared in accordance with Postnord rules, so we have automatically refunded you for your purchase!

Sometimes, merchants have already shipped your package. If this is the case, you may receive a message from Postnord to pay VAT and the handling fee. Since you have already been refunded, you will have two options:

1. If you don't want your item, then do nothing & ignore the messages. OR.
2. If you do want your item, contact Postnord with your order ID and they will release the package free of charge. That means we’ve covered your whole purchase, shipping fees & Postnord VAT for you!

We apologize for any inconvenience and are working round the clock to make sure all 1 million merchants follow Postnord rules in the future!

Për porositë e dhëna para 1 korrikut 202.source_string: For orders placed prior to July 1, 2021, VAT wasn't included in the total price of your order. Due to this, your item may be held at customs until the VAT is paid. We've got your back if this happens - please pay for the VAT and we'll give you a refund for it (up to 25% of the original item price). After paying the VAT, reach out to our support team to request your refund. Select 'Learn more' below for instructions to contact us.

Për shembull, nëse bëhet një porosi dhe.source_string: For example, if an order is placed and payment received on 31st December 2020 then the new rules will not apply, even if dispatch and delivery take place after 1 January 2021.  Therefore, for imports, the consignment will remain subject to import VAT (unless it is below the Low-Value Consignment Relief threshold of £15) and supply VAT should not be charged. For goods already in the UK at the time of supply, the VAT liability will remain with the seller rather than Wish.

Përqindja e zbritur dhe shumat e kursime.source_string:
Percentage off and savings amounts are based on the seller's reference price.  Sellers are not required to provide a reference price, but if they do, it should be (a) the Manufacturer's Suggested Retail Price (MSRP) or similar List Price of the product; or (b) the price at which the item has been recently offered for sale and for a reasonable period of time.
The reference price can give you an indication of the value of the product butsome stores may sell the item for less than the reference price.

If you feel a reference price is inaccurate or misleading please report it with the URL for the listing to report-abuse@wish.com.

Hi

We’re writing to let you know that we were recently informed that one or more item(s) you have purchased does not meet applicable content or safety standards/regulations, due to missing instructional manual in local language.

Përshëndetje {%1=customer name}\n\nFalem.source_string:
Hello {%1=customer name}

Thank you for providing this information.

We have refunded this charge back to your account. Please allow up to 10 business days for the refunds to process. We apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused you.

Please let us know if we can assist you further.

Hello {%1=customer name}

Thank you for getting in touch with us and I appreciate your patience as I verified your account. I've gone ahead and removed the hold on your account.

For next steps, I recommend reviewing your recent orders as some may not have been processed during this hold. Should you still want any of the items from a cancelled order, you'll need to re-order them through the app.

We appreciate your understanding in this matter.

Hello {%1=customer name}

Thank you for reaching out to us.

We have received your request to update one of your account settings below.

Please provide a copy of your photo ID and the information you want to change so we can assist you in updating your account.

Email:
Reset Password: (Yes/No)
Phone:

We look forward to your reply.

Hello {%1=customer name}

Thank you for contacting us.

To ensure your account security, we logged you out of your Wish account and issued a separate password reset to your email address.

To change your password, simply click on the reset link in the email. We strongly recommend choosing a password you haven't used before on any other online platform.

Once logged in, please review your payment and address settings to verify your information. You should also be able to shop on Wish and access your order history.

Hello {%1=customer name}

Thank you for contacting us.

Përshëndetje,\n\nWish ka marrë njoftimin.source_string:
Hello,

Wish has received the enclosed California Proposition 65 notice regarding your product(s). A California Proposition 65 violation can constitute a violation of Wish’s Terms of Use (see sec. 5 para. 6) and Wish policies; see, e.g.: Wish Merchant Policy 7.20.

What is Proposition 65?

Proposition 65 is a ballot initiative passed by California voters in 1986, is a toxic chemicals right-to-know law requiring a company doing business in California to place warnings on products and, if the product is sold on the internet, on web pages featuring the product.  The law requires the warning when certain chemicals in the products are present in levels that could cause certain levels of exposure to the consumer. 

The law allows private enforcers to bring notices of violation of any of 950 chemicals it regulates, which in turn requires the company, as one option, to add warnings that the product at issue contains specific chemicals that can cause cancer or reproductive harm.  Another option is to withdraw the product from California sale. Neither option exempts the company from liability for the period of time the product was sold to California consumers without a warning.  The warning must be both on the product packaging and on the Wish web page where the product is featured.

Actions Taken by Wish

In response to this report, Wish has reviewed the applicable listing(s) for non-compliance and the following product listing(s) was removed from the platform in all applicable jurisdictions:

{%1=app name} kërkon vazhdimisht mënyra.source_string: {%1=app name} is constantly looking for ways to gather and present information about merchants and their items to help users make informed choices. In {%1=app name}'s Premier Merchant Program, merchant performance across a variety of metrics is tracked in an automated way, and if it meets or exceeds certain thresholds, merchants are eligible for the Premier badge. User ratings of the merchant and the merchant's items, refunds, fulfillment, and compliance with {%1=app name} policies are some of the more notable groups of elements that are tracked. When {%1=app name} shows the badge and a brief description, we may highlight a few areas that reflect merchant performance in specific categories such as item quality, fulfillment & shipping, and customer satisfaction. The formula or approach for monitoring and reporting on merchant performance, including performance areas and minimum scores, may be updated over time.

{%1=app name} nuk jua shet të dhënat për.source_string: {%1=app name} does not sell your data for money. {%1=app name} does share data about app activity, such as purchases, with companies and service providers in the advertising ecosystem in ways that may be considered a sale under CCPA. The shared data is associated with a number such as an Ad ID, not your name. If you wish to opt-out of such sharing toggle the appropriate selector to "off"
